        " أَبُو جَعْفَرٍ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : «مَنْ صَلَّى عِنْدَ اَلْمَقَامِ رَكْعَتَيْنِ عَدَلَتَا عِتْقَ سِتِّ نَسَمَاتٍ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2155 - Abu Ja’far (as) said:\n\"Whoever prays two Rak’ahs at the Station of Ibrahim, it is equivalent to freeing six souls.\""
        ]
